    <p>If you want a stronger cup, a bigger mug, or a mellower dark-roast brew, the “best” ratio shifts fast. That is the whole trick with AeroPress. You are not chasing one magic number. You are choosing the ratio that matches the kind of cup you want to drink tomorrow morning.</p>
